e to" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 27 "achieve this automatically." }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 47 "Firstly, \+
fit needs lists of x and y separately." }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 
1 0 43 "xli := seq(log(li[i][1]), i=1..nops([li]));" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 
